<HEAD>Shots Fired at U.S. Library in Philippines</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Three armed men opened fire on the
U.S. Information Service library in Davao City on Sunday,
shattering windows but causing no injuries, police reported.
   Sgt. Rommel Moya said the gunmen escaped after shooting from a
speeding car about 1:15 p.m. The library was closed at the time,
